## <a id="reqs"></a> Requirements

<%= vars.product_short %> has the following requirements:

* You must be signed up to the <%= vars.product_short %> Early Adopter Programme
* A Kubernetes cluster configured in
[OIDC mode](https://docs.pivotal.io/pks/manage-cluster-permissions.html#cluster-access-user)
* A sandbox environment for testing
* A Docker image registry that images can be relocated to

## <a id="limitations"></a> Limitations

### <a id="gen-lim"></a> General Limitations

* This product is in alpha. The structure of the product is fully subject to change in further alphas or later releases. Pivotal does not provide commercial support for its alpha products.
* This product is intended to be used with any Kubernetes distribution. However, given the number of
Kubernetes vendors, versions, and configurations, not all of them have been tested with
<%= vars.product_abbr %>.
* Product upgrades are currently not supported. To test a newer version, delete the previous version first.

